The files in this directory can be used to build a docker image that
will run a Riak server as well as an sshd.

Building the image:
  sudo docker build -t "<your_name>/skydns" .

Listing the images:
  sudo docker images

Start the image in daemon mode with:
  sudo docker run -d -p 53:53 -p 8080:8080 -p 10122:22 <your_name>/skydns

Use SSH to connect to the instance, root password is "password".